data.description:
Experience the joy of country living in this mini farm retreat - a place where the simplicity of nature meets the comforts of home. This property is not just a house; it's an invitation to embrace a lifestyle that values tranquility, space, and the beauty of rural living. Welcome to your new haven in the heart of Callahan only 22 minutes from the Jacksonville International Airport!

Nestled on a spacious 2.45 acre property, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and rustic elegance. With 3 bedrooms and 2 1/2 baths on the first floor, this residence is designed to accommodate the needs of a modern family.

Step inside to discover a welcoming atmosphere, where the heart of the home lies in the spacious eat-in kitchen that becomes the central hub for creating lasting memories. 

This split bedroom layout offers privacy between shared spaces and personal retreats. The master suite is a refuge of relaxation with its own jetted garden tub and separate tiled shower.

Extra wide stairs lead to the 2nd floor bonus room adding versatility to the property, offering a flexible space that can be tailored to suit your needs.

Recent updates include new roof (8/2023), new water heater (11/2022), hurricane rated Pole Barn (2017), new carpet and paint inside and out, enhancing the natural beauty of the surrounding countryside.
